Introduction
Welcome to Slide Dish, a mobile application provided by nevr.app s.r.o ("we," "us," or "our"). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application.
Information We Collect
Personal Information
: We may collect personal information that you provide directly, such as your name, email address, country and other contact information.
Device Information
: We may automatically collect information about your mobile device, including your device type, operating system, unique device identifiers, and mobile network information.
Usage Information
: We may collect information about how you use our app, such as the features you access and the actions you take.
Location Information
: With your consent, we may collect and process information about your device's location.
How We Use Your Information
We may use the information we collect for various purposes, including:
To provide and maintain our app.
To improve our app and develop new features.
To respond to your requests, comments, or questions.
To send you updates, newsletters, and marketing communications (if you have opted in).
Sharing of Your Information
We may share your information with third parties in the following circumstances:
With service providers and partners who assist us in delivering our app.
With law enforcement, regulatory authorities, or legal processes when required by applicable law.
User-Uploaded Content
Users of Slide Dish may have the option to upload and share their own culinary creations, including dishes, recipes, photos, and other multimedia content. We value your creativity and engagement with our app. However, please be aware of the following:
Ownership and Authorship
: You must be the author and rightful owner of any content you upload to Slide Dish. By uploading content, you represent and warrant that you have the necessary rights and permissions to share it on our platform. Do not upload dishes from restaurants or the internet that are not your own creations.
Usage for Marketing Purposes
: We may use the uploaded multimedia files, including photos and descriptions of dishes, for marketing and promotional purposes related to Slide Dish. This may include featuring user-generated content on our website, social media profiles, or in advertising materials. Rest assured that we will do so in compliance with applicable laws and with respect to your rights.
User-Generated Content Guidelines
: We encourage you to follow our user-generated content guidelines, which may be outlined in a separate document or section of the app. These guidelines may cover topics such as appropriate content, copyright infringement, and community standards.
Content Removal
: If you wish to have your uploaded content removed from Slide Dish or if you believe your intellectual property rights have been infringed upon by a user, please contact us at
we@nevr.app
, and we will address your request promptly.
Please remember that user-generated content is subject to review, and we reserve the right to remove or take down any content that violates our terms of service, content guidelines, or applicable laws.
By uploading content to Slide Dish, you acknowledge and agree to these terms regarding user-uploaded content.
Health Disclaimer
We are not responsible for any health problems associated with imitating food from the app. While we strive to provide accurate and reliable information, the preparation and consumption of food may carry inherent risks. It is essential to exercise caution and consult with a healthcare professional or nutritionist if you have specific dietary concerns or health conditions.
Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
Children's Privacy
Our app is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or maintain information from children under 13 years of age.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes to our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at
we@nevr.app
.
